                        <p>The Storey Social is a social media consultancy specialising in the publishing industry that can help you, and your books, get noticed on social media. I grew up online. I created a fashion and lifestyle blog when I was just fourteen and have been active on all forms of social media ever since. The Storey Social wants to help you and your books stand out on social media.</p>
