                        <h2 class="mt-5 title">Christina Storey</h2>
                        <p>After graduating from Queen Mary University of London with a 2.1 in English Literature in 2018 I immediately became a part time Bookseller at my local Waterstones. Within four months I was promoted to a full time Senior Bookseller. When at Waterstones I fully immersed myself in the Publishing world; I set up the bookshops Instagram and helped out with their Twitter.</p>
                        <p>I spent 2019 working and travelling in Australia and came back to England in 2020 eager to get a job in the publishing industry. Covid-19 has delayed this. In response to the freeze on hiring I have launched my own social media projects, and these are now listed under the umbrella of The Storey Social.</p>
